{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"71f764c7-a933-4e8e-87a6-450fd74f2fc6","content":"Yes, you'll hit **compatibility issues** with your current target frameworks. MSTest v3 dropped support for:\n\n- **`net5.0`** — .NET 5 is no longer supported; you need **.NET 6+**\n- **`net462`** — .NET Framework older than 4.6.2 is the minimum, so `net462` is borderline (it's the lowest supported). Double-check it works, but `net472` is safer.\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — .NET Core 3.1 is **no longer supported**; you need **.NET 6+**\n\n**Summary of required changes:**\n\n| Current TFM | Action |\n|---|---|\n| `net5.0` | Upgrade to `net6.0` or later |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | Upgrade to `net6.0` or later |\n| `net462` | OK (minimum supported), but consider `net472`+ |\n\nWould you like me to run the full MSTest v3 migration on this project (updating TFMs and packages)?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5bedd83b-7b05-403d-9b3e-dd5870dcdb31","outputTokens":257,"requestId":"BC2B:BD0FA:21785EB:2542E23:69FAA838"},"id":"7dbb9aae-da7a-4af8-b2b2-082c1ef2c1bd","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:32:30.473Z","parentId":"c4ffda7a-c16e-4227-b13c-430ecf9e4f74"}
